 steps for Java Configuration of Spring beans:
 
 1. create a java class and annotate as @Configuration
 2. Add component scanning support @ComponentScan(">>>Add the package name here<<<");
 3. Read Spring Java configuration class
 4. Retrieve bean from Spring container.
 
 Reading spring java configuration class
 AnnotationConfigApplicationContext context =
 									new  AnnotationConfigApplicationContext(<className>.class);
 									
 	